      "content": "but that's the thing... it doesn't feel like I'm part of some tapestry. it feels like i'm just consuming space. like i'm just a void where a person should be. if i just... went away, there wouldn't even be a hole left behind. it wouldn't even be a loss, it would just be a quietness.",
